  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Establishes a Mohawk River Basin district and Mohawk River Basin management program for management of such district to preserve, protect, restore and enhance the environmental quality of the Mohawk River."
